## `$ tree src/`

```text
app/
 ├── (auth)/
 │   ├── login/      → Login com OTP
 │   └── register/   → Cadastro 15 etapas
 ├── (app)/
 │   ├── feed/       → Swipe de descoberta
 │   ├── matches/    → Matches e chat
 │   ├── events/     → Eventos e participantes
 │   └── profile/    → Perfil e conquistas
 └── api/            → REST API (auth, users, swipe, matches, events)
components/          → Componentes reutilizáveis (AppShell, etc)
context/             → AppContext (Estado global)
lib/                 → auth, email, match-algorithm
prisma/              → schema.prisma (MySQL) & seed.ts
```

